title: Vikram
subTitle: A special agent investigates a murder committed by a masked group of serial killers. However, a tangled maze of clues soon leads him to the drug kingpin of Chennai.

title: Goal
subTitle: Sam, a football player, gets admission in a prestigious international school under sports quota. His life changes for the better when he falls in love with a girl from the same school.

title: Kili Poyi
subTitle: Friends Chacko and Hari are fed up with their employer and plan a trip to Goa. Their trip turns into something unusual when they discover a mysterious bag.

title: London Bridge
subTitle: Vijay's life takes an unexpected turn when he falls for Merin. However, he is already betrothed to Pavithra, the daughter of an affluent man.

title: Vinodayathra
subTitle: Vinod, a quarrelsome young man, moves into his sister's house in a village to get his life in order. There, he happens to meet Anupama and falls in love with her.

title: Mambazhakkalam
subTitle: When his father dies, Chandran is forced to go abroad to earn money to pay his father's dues. On a holiday to India, he meets his childhood lover and hopes to rekindle the relationship.

title: Srungaravelan
subTitle: Kanan falls in love with Raddhu, the daughter of a ruthless city gangster responsible for numerous deaths. To marry her, Kanan must confront the dangers and challenges that lie ahead.

title: Classmates
subTitle: A group of college friends meet after many years for a class reunion. However, due to some unexpected turn of events, several dark secrets are revealed, which changes their lives.

title: Lucky Baskhar
subTitle: Desperate to bring his family out of monetary woes, Baskhar Kumar, a bank employee, enters the dangerous and murky world of financial scams.

title: Nadiya Kollappetta Rathri
subTitle: When a television reporter, a shooter and a dancer get murdered on a train, an encounter specialist is called upon to investigate the three murders that seem to be unconnected to one another.

title: Nadiya Kollappetta Rathri

title: Sarkkar Colony
subTitle: Life in a modest government colony takes a turn as its residents pursue a side venture, hoping to ease financial burdens but ending up in unexpected chaos.

title: Olu
subTitle: A girl's spirit connects with a struggling painter, infusing his art with divine inspiration. Their love transcends earthly boundaries yet faces a perilous test when worldly temptations beckon.

title: Sudani From Nigeria
subTitle: Majeed, a football coach in Malappuram, recuits Nigerian players for his local team. When star player Samuel is injured, he stays with Majeed, leading to a deep bond despite cultural differences.

title: Sreekrishnapurathe Nakshathrathilakkam
subTitle: Three out of four brothers of a Malayali household are happily married while the fourth brother is engaged. When the beautiful Yamuna Rani becomes their new neighbour, she poses a threat to the wives.

title: Premam
subTitle: Vikram falls in love with different women at various stages of his life and with each experience, he bears the pain and emotions of separation.

title: Neyyattinkara Gopante Aaraattu
subTitle: An affluent man is called upon to hand over his vast plot of land to the government. However, situations take a turn when he brings the influential Neyyattinkara Gopan into the picture.

title: K.G.F: Chapter 1
subTitle: Rocky, a young man, seeks power and wealth in order to fulfil a promise to his dying mother. His quest takes him to Mumbai, where he gets involved with the notorious gold mafia.

title: Guruvayur Ambalanadayil
subTitle: A young man eagerly awaits his wedding, but fate twists cruelly, forcing him into a lifelong bond with a woman who harbours nothing but resentment for him.

title: Janatha Garage
subTitle: When Anand visits Hyderabad, he encounters Sathyam, who operates an organisation aiding the underprivileged. Sathyam, swayed by Anand's vision, hands over the organisation's management to him.

title: Thinkal Muthal Velli Vare
subTitle: A famous television scriptwriter vows never to get married. However, he is forced into marriage by one of his ardent fans who threatens to commit suicide if he does not marry her.

title: Bichakaran 2
subTitle: Sathya is a poor man in search of his sister, who has been kidnapped by human traffickers. However, an illegal brain transplant puts him in the shoes of a billionaire named Vijay.

title: Kadal Kadannu Oru Maathukutty
subTitle: An unemployed man living in Germany receives an opportunity to organise a star-studded event in Kerala. However, chaos ensues when he arrives in the country.

title: Chess
subTitle: A man murders his rich brother-in-law with the help of three co-conspirators to amass his wealth. He also manages to discredit the deceased man's illegitimate son.

title: Kalippattam
subTitle: A violinist enters a marriage that promises security, only to face heartbreak as love, illness and time reshape everything he once believed was under control.

title: Bangalore Days
subTitle: Three cousins, Divya, Krishnan and Arjuna, share a close bond and decide to move to Bangalore to fulfil their childhood dreams. There, they face challenges that will change their lives forever.

title: Ittymaani: Made in China
subTitle: Ittymaani, who was raised in China, runs a business of counterfeit products in India. However, when he tries to help Annamma who is ignored by her sons, he lands in trouble because she falls ill.

title: 2 Countries
subTitle: Ullas, a money-minded man, agrees to marry a woman with disabilities, Simran, eyeing her wealth. When he gets a proposal from a woman with better prospects, he leaves Simran for her.

title: Love Action Drama
subTitle: Dinesh, a conceited and wealthy young bachelor, goes to extreme lengths to impress a girl named Shobha with the help of his best friend Sagar, and Dinesh eventually hopes to marry Shobha.
